
This contains the OpenGL previewer for the input file to your raytracer.

Makefile: Linux Makefile
openglviewer.cpp source code
openglviewer Linux executable
openglviewer.exe Windows executable
viewer/ Visual C++ environment; viewer.dsw = workspace
testscenes/ Test scenes: scene1, scene2, scene3 
	    These scenes are documented and also have multiple camera
            positions you should try

 